Title: Proceedings: ML95 Workshop on `Agents that Learn from Other Agents'
Body: Meanwhile, there is also an active interest in agents that learn from observation (e.g., Iba 1991, Lin 1993), as well as agents that communicate and learn from each other (e.g., Etzioni & Weld 1994, Lashkari, Metral, & Maes 1994, Tan 1993).
